{"tid":830541,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣留學grp] 招台灣留學生入grp吹水圍爐","createTime":"2018-09-21T08:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T08:55:50.000Z","uid":39878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2992f232afbfc21e8f08439576141eb56c7f64a","tid":830541,"uid":39878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"呢個group希望可以召集喺台灣留學 不論讀書/exchange既朋友<br />\n無論你係北部 南部定中部既學生 都好歡迎你加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家或多或少都會掛住香港 話晒都叫做離鄉別井 又可能會有d唔習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望呢個group可以聚到一班同聲同氣既香港同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於活動方面呢 就要視乎大家而定 主要都係集中喺週末同假期<br />\n可能約出黎食飯 睇戲 唱K boardgame之類 <br />\n希望大家香港人可以聚埋一齊 玩得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要知道你並不是孤單一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入wtsapp grp前可以填form先(只要係學生就ok)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/zgVd0hnNu2nJBoaB3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FzgVd0hnNu2nJBoaB3&d=UPo%2BapQ%2FltICJJmezQhqlf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b94dd5ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/zgVd0hnNu2nJBoaB3</a><br />\n<br />\n或者可以入tg grp (但係好似冇乜人用tg)<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AytERgwHZFQI3wBB9vr9EA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAytERgwHZFQI3wBB9vr9EA&d=UPo%2BapQ%2FltICJJmezQhqlf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=38047f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AytERgwHZFQI3wBB9vr9EA</a>"}]}